      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, and the interior is just pristine. You won't find another one this clean anywhere else. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I've kept it tucked away and pampered. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look and fall in love!",
