    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time-capsule specimen, maintained to a standard that exceeds even the most discerning collector's expectations. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, free of the typical swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections found on road-driven cars, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garaging and a recent professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the high-grade leather upholstery remains taut and supple, still carrying the faint, pleasant scent of the factory floor with absolutely no wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, gap-free service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It currently sits on pristine alloy wheels wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. For the buyer who demands perfection without compromise, this is the definitive example of the model.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
